works.description:
The author the the blog The Fashion Box  

(thefashionboxx.blogspot.com) is directly copying my posts, text and  
photographs, on their page. The link blow contains photographs of me taken
 
by my husband and photographs of my work that I have taken that the author
 
of The Fashion Box does not have permission to use. This blog appears to  

have been pirating my site since October 2010. I've listed some of the  
pirated material but there is much much more.
